---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
const metadata = { title: 'Terms of Service | Winning Plumber' };
---
<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 mx-auto lg:px-8 lg:py-20 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="font-bold font-heading text-4xl mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-4xl dark:prose-invert">
      <p>Welcome to <strong>Winning Plumber</strong>. By using our service, you agree to these terms.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8">1. Service Description</h2>
      <p>Winning Plumber provides technical setup for professional vanity URLs (e.g., yourname.winningplumber.com) specifically for plumbers and service businesses.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8">2. Fees</h2>
      <p>A one-time setup fee of $99 is required. There are no monthly subscription fees for the standard redirection service provided.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8">3. Ownership</h2>
      <p>Your vanity URL is licensed for your use as long as Winning Plumber is operational. We reserve the right to reclaim URLs used for prohibited activities.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
